OL,5, Special paid leave for Covid-related   
OL,6, sickness and isolation will be scrapped
OL,7, next week for NHS staff in England, it 
OL,8, has been announced.                    
OL,10,FFrom 7 July staff will revert to normal
OL,11,Fcontractual sick pay arrangements.     
OL,13,FThe Royal College of Nursing (RCN) said
OL,14,Fthe decision was "hugely disappointing"
OL,15,Fand indicated "how little" the         
OL,16,Fgovernment valued its staff.           
OL,18,FThe Department of Health and Social    
OL,19,FCare (DHSC) said the changes were part 
OL,20,Fof learning to live with Covid.        
